Pushpin.MapIconInfoContent: Used to mark key locations so that adventurers don't miss anything important.

Icon_cangbaotu.MapIconInfoContent: Collect Omnium scattered underground and obtain awesome rewards the next day.

WorldBoss.MapIconInfoContent: Hykros had no choice but to cut off contact with other regions. Omnium twisted the minds of almost all creatures. The station on the border has been facing an ever-growing siege, as the constant invaders must be stopped...

AstralPortal.MapIconInfoContent: The entrance of the Star Realm leads to an area that can't be observed directly from the continent and has mysterious hostile creatures and unexpected treasure.

SpecialAstralPortal.MapIconInfoContent: The entrance of the Star Realm leads to an area that can't be observed directly from the continent and has mysterious hostile creatures and unexpected treasure.

huiyu_plane.MapIconInfoContent:
There is an unstable spatial rift in Vera. Through the rift, one can briefly enter the plane that Mirroria refers to as the "Grayspace."
<LblRed13>It turns out that the Grayspace Fissure cannot be spotted from within the Grayspace</>.
